Baldur’s Gate 3 is a new turn-based fantasy RPG. Even though this is a third game in the series, the game’s plot has no correlation to previous entries, so don’t be afraid to get lost in the history of this world, if you’re unfamiliar with this universe. First, you’ll get to create your character, and you can spend more than an hour customizing and fine-tuning your avatar. You can choose from 11 races and 28 subraces and pick one of the 12 classes and 48 subclasses. Any race can pick up any class, so you are not restricted in your choice. Elves, humans, tieflings, githyanki, halflings and other races can be wizards, druids, rangers, clerics, etc. Your choice will not only influence your appearance, but also your stats, your lineage and how other characters will treat you. If you want to create the elf of your dreams make them romance a bear then all you need to do is buy Baldur’s Gate 3 key!

In the game you’ll visit the vast world of the Forgotten Reams universe. Explore the continent of Faerûn and its regions, such as the Underdark, the home to many Drows. Go down to the Hells and survive in Avernus. Escape the Nautiloid and fight off illithids. There are lots of locations to explore, each with their own cast of interesting characters, quests, dungeons and, of course, treasures to find; if you dare to fight off whatever is protecting them, of course. Only one playthrough could take you 80 hours, but for completionists, striving to uncover every secret and find every item, the playtime might even double! You can talk to almost every NPC in the game. That includes your companions, with which you may grow closer together or grow apart. If right choices are made, you can even romance them. The game features more than 2 million words to listen to during the dialogues and more than 147 hours of cinematics to watch. If you’re a fan of old-school RPGs or just tired of same, uninspired games that have been emerging lately, then you definitely should buy Baldur’s Gate 3 key. The game can easily pull you in and stay in your memories for long!
